OL,3,CIgor Tudor leaves Tottenham after
OL,4,Cseven games as head coach
OL,6,FIgor Tudor has left his role as
OL,7,FTottenham head coach after seven
OL,8,Fmatches in charge.
OL,10,FSpurs made the surprise decision to
OL,11,Fturn to the Croatian after Thomas
OL,12,FFrank was dismissed on February 11.
OL,14,FTudor had never managed in the Premier
OL,15,FLeague, but had experience of sparking
OL,16,Fan upturn in form after mid-season
OL,17,Farrivals and yet suffered five defeats
OL,18,Ffrom seven games, including four in a
OL,19,Frow at the start of his reign.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
