OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774887078
OL,3,CIgor Tudor leaves Tottenham after
OL,4,Cseven games as head coach
OL,6,FA club statement on Sunday afternoon
OL,7,Fread: "We can confirm that it has been
OL,8,Fmutually agreed for head coach Igor
OL,9,FTudor to leave the club with immediate
OL,10,Feffect.
OL,12,F"Tomislav Rogic and Riccardo Ragnacci
OL,13,Fhave also left their respective roles
OL,14,Fof goalkeeping coach and physical
OL,15,Fcoach.
OL,17,F"We thank Igor, Tomislav and Riccardo
OL,18,Ffor their efforts during the past six
OL,19,Fweeks, in which they worked tirelessly.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
