CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774887078
OL,3,CIgor Tudor leaves Tottenham after
OL,4,Cseven games as head coach
OL,6,FWe also acknowledge the bereavement
OL,7,Fthat Igor has recently suffered and
OL,8,Fsend our support to him and his family
OL,9,Fat this difficult time.
OL,11,F"An update on a new head coach will be
OL,12,Fprovided in due course."
OL,14,FThe most recent defeat came at home to
OL,15,FNottingham Forest on March 22, prior
OL,16,Fto the international break.
OL,18,FImmediately after that game, the 47-
OL,19,Fyear-old learned his father Mario had
OL,20,Fdied.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
