OL,3,CIgor Tudor leaves Tottenham after
OL,4,Cseven games as head coach
OL,6,FTudor's exit leaves Spurs without a
OL,7,Fhead coach heading into the final
OL,8,Fseven games of the Premier League
OL,9,Fseason, with the London club just one
OL,10,Fplace and one point above the
OL,11,Frelegation zone.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
