OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774887078
OL,3,CIgor Tudor leaves Tottenham after
OL,4,Cseven games as head coach
OL,6,FAssistant Bruno Saltor will lead
OL,7,Ftraining for the players not away on
OL,8,Finternational duty at the moment, the
OL,9,FPress Association understands, with
OL,10,Fthe club aiming to appoint a new head
OL,11,Fcoach in the coming days, in time for
OL,12,Fthe full squad being back together and
OL,13,Fa crucial 10-day preparation period
OL,14,Fahead of the April 12 fixture at
OL,15,FSunderland.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
