OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774887078
OL,3,CIgor Tudor leaves Tottenham after
OL,4,Cseven games as head coach
OL,6,FFormer Brighton boss Roberto De Zerbi
OL,7,Fand ex-Burnley and Everton manager
OL,8,FSean Dyche are among the bookmakers'
OL,9,Ffavourites to take over, or they could
OL,10,Fturn to Ryan Mason, boyhood Spurs fan
OL,11,Fand player who has twice been
OL,12,Fcaretaker before.
OL,14,FTottenham Hotspur Supporters' Trust
OL,15,Fresponded to the news of Tudor's
OL,16,Fdeparture by urging the club to now
OL,17,Fmake a "wise choice" regarding his
OL,18,Freplacement.
OL,26,@yD@HOUyD@TO]
