CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774887078
OL,3,CIgor Tudor leaves Tottenham after
OL,4,Cseven games as head coach
OL,6,FIts post on X read: "With thanks to
OL,7,FIgor and his team for their efforts,
OL,8,Fand wishing him and his family time to
OL,9,Fcome to terms with their loss.
OL,11,F"In a season of bad calls, let's hope
OL,12,Fwe now see a wise choice for the
OL,13,Fremainder of the campaign.
OL,15,F"Someone who understands the club and
OL,16,Fis up to the task in front of them:
OL,17,Fretaining our Premier League status.
OL,18,FSomeone we can all be proud of and who
OL,19,Fcan bring some much needed success and
OL,20,Fenjoyment to our long suffering
OL,21,Ffanbase."
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUwD@AOU}D@IO]
